# Privacy Statement

## HarmonyTuner Privacy Policy

### Data Collection
HarmonyTuner does not collect any personal data. All tuning records are stored locally on your device.

### Microphone Usage
The microphone is used solely for real-time pitch detection. Audio data is processed in real-time and is not stored or transmitted.

### Data Storage
- Tuning history is stored in device local storage only
- No data is transmitted to any server
- No user account or authentication is required

### Contact
For privacy concerns, please contact the developer.
